{
  "total_duration": 702.796,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.2,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象一个小村庄。村里有个大家都认识的人，叫 Sam Benton。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 5.55,
      "end": 14.55,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Sam 是本地 butcher，也就是卖肉的店主。这样的人在小村庄里不是陌生人，大家买东西会见到他，路上也会打招呼。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 14.9,
      "end": 26.54,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有一天，Sam 带着自己攒下来的 savings 去 post office。这里的 savings 是存款，post office 在老式社区里也可能处理一些钱款服务。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 26.89,
      "end": 31.69,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结果，钱包丢了。不是几枚硬币，而是一大笔钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 32.039,
      "end": 36.92,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "村子很小，消息很快传开：Sam 的钱不见了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 37.269,
      "end": 45.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Sam 心里也明白，这钱包大概不是掉进河里了，而是被村里某个人捡到了。可是，没有人来还。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 46.179,
      "end": 53.059,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "三个月后，一个早晨，Sam 打开门，发现门口放着一个用报纸包起来的钱包。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 53.409,
      "end": 65.409,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "钱包回来了，但里面只有一半的钱，还有一张纸条。那个人好像在跟自己的良心谈判：我是小偷，是的，但我只是 50 per cent a thief。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 65.759,
      "end": 71.319,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是今天的题目：A clear conscience，问心无愧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 71.669,
      "end": 79.629,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Conscience 可以理解成心里的良心声音。A clear conscience 就是心里没有亏欠，晚上能睡得踏实。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 79.979,
      "end": 87.699,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是这篇课文的笑点就在这里：钱可以分期还，诚实真的能分期变回来吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 88.049,
      "end": 109.089,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天背诵不要先硬背一长串英文。先记中文电影线：全村知道丢钱 -> Sam 丢钱包 -> 带 savings 去 post office -> 觉得有人捡了但没还 -> 三个月后钱包回来一半 -> 50% 小偷 -> 又还一些 -> 25% 小偷 -> 最后全还清 -> 100% honest。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 109.438,
      "end": 111.758,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一段，丢钱传开。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 112.108,
      "end": 116.988,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：全村都知道，Sam 丢了一大笔钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 117.338,
      "end": 124.018,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对应的英文块是：The whole village soon learnt，还有 a large sum of money had been lost。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 124.368,
      "end": 131.748,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "A large sum of money 是一大笔钱。Had been lost 是过去完成被动，重点放在钱已经丢了这个结果上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 132.098,
      "end": 137.978,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后人物出现：Sam Benton, the local butcher, had lost his wallet。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 138.328,
      "end": 146.688,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Local butcher 是本地卖肉的店主。这个背景很重要，因为小村庄里大家认识他，所以消息会传得很快。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 147.038,
      "end": 149.358,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二段，钱包没有回来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 149.708,
      "end": 157.228,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：Sam 带着 savings 去 post office，觉得钱包肯定被村民捡到了，可是没人还。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 157.578,
      "end": 164.498,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先挂住两个英文块：while taking his savings to the post office，和 must have been found。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 164.847,
      "end": 174.287,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Must have been found 的意思是：Sam 没看见是谁捡的，但他很肯定，钱包一定已经被人捡到了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 174.637,
      "end": 180.757,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "形式是 must have been 加过去分词，表示对过去被动事件的高把握推测。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 181.107,
      "end": 186.867,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面还有一句很关键：it was not returned to him。钱包没有被还给他。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 187.217,
      "end": 192.297,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是本课的 mystery grammar：我们知道发生了什么，却不知道是谁做的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 192.647,
      "end": 196.127,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三段，第一次良心分期。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 196.477,
      "end": 204.677,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：三个月后，钱包出现在 Sam 家门口，被报纸包着，里面只有一半的钱和一张纸条。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 205.027,
      "end": 212.987,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对应英文块是：Three months passed，outside his front door，wrapped up in newspaper，contained half the money。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 213.336,
      "end": 221.056,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Wrapped up in newspaper 是用报纸包起来。Contained half the money 是里面有一半的钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 221.406,
      "end": 226.446,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接下来纸条出现了：A thief, yes, but only 50 per cent a thief!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 226.796,
      "end": 236.036,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话的中文意思不是说偷东西可以原谅，而是在制造一个荒唐笑点：他还了一半钱，就说自己只是 50% 小偷。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 236.386,
      "end": 242.666,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但 returning half is not enough。还一半不是诚实，只是开始补错。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 243.016,
      "end": 245.056,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四段，逐步还清。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 245.406,
      "end": 255.526,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：又过两个月，又有一些钱送来；最后 Sam 的钱全还清了，那个人说自己 100% honest。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 255.876,
      "end": 260.796,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先记 Two months later，再记 some more money was sent。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 261.146,
      "end": 265.346,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Was sent 还是被动语态，因为送来钱的人继续匿名。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 265.696,
      "end": 269.616,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二张纸条说：Only 25 per cent a thief now!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 269.965,
      "end": 277.165,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后是 all Sam's money was paid back，还有 I am 100 per cent honest now!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 277.515,
      "end": 282.555,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个结尾很 New Concept：有点干，有点好笑，也有点刺人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 282.905,
      "end": 288.365,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他想把良心像欠款一样分期还清，可是真正的诚实不是百分比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 288.715,
      "end": 292.997,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老师，最后他把钱都还了，那是不是就问心无愧了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 293.347,
      "end": 300.387,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他确实做了一件该做的事：把钱还回去。但一开始拿走别人的钱，还是错的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 300.737,
      "end": 304.427,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以课文不是在说“偷了以后慢慢还也行”？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 304.777,
      "end": 312.617,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，完全不是。笑点是那个人给自己的良心算百分比，好像还一半就只剩一半的小偷。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 312.967,
      "end": 315.347,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Honesty 不是考试分数。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 315.697,
      "end": 324.297,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Exactly. Honesty is not a percentage score。诚实不是 50%、25%、100% 这样算出来的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 324.647,
      "end": 327.275,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那 clear conscience 到底是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 327.625,
      "end": 334.985,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是你知道自己没有亏欠，或者已经认真把错事补好了，所以心里干净、踏实。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 335.335,
      "end": 338.159,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇为什么这么多被动语态？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 338.509,
      "end": 350.149,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为做事的人一直躲在故事背后。钱 had been lost，钱包 must have been found，钱 was sent，最后 was paid back。我们看见结果，却看不见那个人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 350.499,
      "end": 353.473,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果现实里我捡到钱包呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 353.822,
      "end": 364.902,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "立刻完整归还。交给老师、前台、保安、警察或者 lost-and-found office。不要只还一部分，更不要给自己算诚实百分比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 365.252,
      "end": 368.515,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The whole village soon learnt that a large sum of money had been lost."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 368.865,
      "end": 374.406,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam Benton, the local butcher, had lost his wallet while taking his savings to the post office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 374.756,
      "end": 380.122,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam was sure that the wallet must have been found by one of the villagers, but it was not returned to him."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 380.472,
      "end": 385.396,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Three months passed, and then one morning, Sam found his wallet outside his front door."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 385.746,
      "end": 394.938,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It had been wrapped up in newspaper and it contained half the money he had lost, together with a note which said: 'A thief, yes, but only 50 per cent a thief!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 395.288,
      "end": 401.174,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Two months later, some more money was sent to Sam with another note: 'Only 25 per cent a thief now!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 401.524,
      "end": 404.667,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In time, all Sam's money was paid back in this way."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 405.017,
      "end": 408.384,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The last note said: 'I am 100 per cent honest now!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 408.734,
      "end": 410.694,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "conscience"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词：conscience。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 411.044,
      "end": 412.521,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "conscience"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "conscience。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 412.871,
      "end": 419.711,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "conscience"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Conscience means the inner sense of right and wrong，心里判断对错的良心声音。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 420.061,
      "end": 427.781,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "conscience"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文标题是 A clear conscience。Clear 在这里不是透明，而是没有内疚、没有亏欠。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 428.131,
      "end": 435.491,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "conscience"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事里的匿名人一开始 conscience is not clear。他一点一点还钱，是因为心里不踏实。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 435.84,
      "end": 442.68,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "conscience"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但真正的 clear conscience 不是靠写百分比纸条得到的，而是靠及时、完整地做对的事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 443.03,
      "end": 444.87,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "savings"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词：savings。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 67,
      "start": 445.22,
      "end": 446.789,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "savings"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "savings。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 447.139,
      "end": 452.859,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "savings"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Savings means money that someone has saved，存下来的钱，存款。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 453.209,
      "end": 459.129,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "savings"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说：Sam had lost his wallet while taking his savings to the post office。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 70,
      "start": 459.479,
      "end": 463.799,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "savings"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句说明 Sam 丢的不是随手零钱，而是重要的钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 71,
      "start": 464.149,
      "end": 475.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "savings"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天我们常用 bank card、banking app、Alipay、WeChat Pay 或 online transfer，但课文里的时代更依赖 cash、wallet 和 post office。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 476.179,
      "end": 477.979,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "villager"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词：villager。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 478.328,
      "end": 479.71,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "villager"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "villager。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 74,
      "start": 480.06,
      "end": 484.26,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "villager"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Villager means a person who lives in a village，村民。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 75,
      "start": 484.61,
      "end": 488.81,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "villager"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说：the wallet must have been found by one of the villagers。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 76,
      "start": 489.16,
      "end": 495.96,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "villager"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个词让故事更 personal。不是大城市里完全陌生的人海，而是一个熟人小社区。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 77,
      "start": 496.31,
      "end": 501.23,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "villager"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也正因为是小村庄，Sam 才会觉得钱包很可能被村里某个人捡到了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 78,
      "start": 501.58,
      "end": 506.34,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar board 叫：被动语态等于匿名故事的语法。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 79,
      "start": 506.69,
      "end": 512.05,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先看这条链：a large sum of money had been lost，钱已经丢了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 80,
      "start": 512.4,
      "end": 516.36,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "The wallet must have been found，钱包一定已经被捡到了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 81,
      "start": 516.71,
      "end": 520.189,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "It was not returned，它没有被还回来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 82,
      "start": 520.539,
      "end": 522.859,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "It had been wrapped up，它被包起来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 83,
      "start": 523.209,
      "end": 526.769,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Some more money was sent，又有钱被送来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 84,
      "start": 527.119,
      "end": 531.319,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "All Sam's money was paid back，所有钱被还清。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 85,
      "start": 531.669,
      "end": 537.469,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么这些句子都适合被动语态？因为我们知道发生了什么，但不知道是谁做的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 86,
      "start": 537.819,
      "end": 544.239,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文把重点放在 wallet、money、note 和 result 上，而不是放在匿名人的脸上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 87,
      "start": 544.589,
      "end": 550.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再看 must have been found。Pattern 是 must have been 加过去分词。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 88,
      "start": 551.179,
      "end": 558.459,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它表达的是：我没有亲眼看见，但我非常确定过去发生了这件事，而且它是被动发生的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 89,
      "start": 558.808,
      "end": 563.168,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如：The door is open. It must have been opened by someone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 90,
      "start": 563.518,
      "end": 567.678,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再比如：The cake is gone. It must have been eaten."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 91,
      "start": 568.028,
      "end": 575.388,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后看百分比笑点：50 per cent a thief，25 per cent a thief，100 per cent honest。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 92,
      "start": 575.738,
      "end": 582.378,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "British English 里 per cent 常常分成两个词；现代日常也会看到 percent 或百分号。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 93,
      "start": 582.728,
      "end": 591.648,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是在这个故事里，百分比不是数学重点，而是 moral joke。钱可以分期还，诚实不能分期算。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 94,
      "start": 591.998,
      "end": 598.638,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把这课放进你的生活。想象你在 school gate 附近发现了一个 wallet，但不知道是谁的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 95,
      "start": 598.988,
      "end": 605.108,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以先用被动语态报告物品：This wallet was found near the school gate."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 96,
      "start": 605.458,
      "end": 610.778,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再用 must have been 做推测：It must have been left by a student."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 97,
      "start": 611.128,
      "end": 616.008,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后说正确做法：I have given it to the school office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 98,
      "start": 616.357,
      "end": 620.677,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果东西都在里面，可以说：Everything is inside."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 99,
      "start": 621.027,
      "end": 625.867,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后加上今天的核心：I want to have a clear conscience."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 100,
      "start": 626.217,
      "end": 633.537,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这和课文里的匿名人不一样。你不是偷偷分期归还，而是 quickly and completely return lost property。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 101,
      "start": 633.887,
      "end": 646.167,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "连起来就是：This wallet was found near the school gate. It must have been left by a student. I have given it to the school office. Everything is inside. I want to have a clear conscience."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 102,
      "start": 646.517,
      "end": 653.837,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 103,
      "start": 654.187,
      "end": 668.547,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "跟读时先抓中文线：全村知道丢钱 -> Sam 丢钱包 -> 没有人还 -> 钱包包着报纸回来一半 -> 50% 小偷 -> 25% 小偷 -> 最后 100% honest。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 104,
      "start": 668.897,
      "end": 678.097,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再把 English chunks 读顺：had been lost，must have been found，was not returned，wrapped up in newspaper，was sent，was paid back。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 105,
      "start": 678.446,
      "end": 690.446,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "跟读完以后，再做 ① 生活场景，练习 honest lost-property return；后面 ② 完形 ③ 中译英 ④ 英译中 ⑤ 默写 一条线做下来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 106,
      "start": 690.796,
      "end": 702.796,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "做完以后，爸爸的邮箱里就会收到你今天的成绩。记住今天的核心：Return what you find, make things right quickly, and do not turn honesty into a percentage game."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "lesson_id": 45
}